I found the puzzle terribly difficult at first, so much so hat I dozed off after two words, then in the morning I roared through the NE to SW diagonal so fast that even though I don’t fret much over speed I regretted all the sleeping time on the clock, but then I stalled for a long time in the NW. Good puzzle IMHO. I didn’t get pwned.

